\[\Pr[X_{i}^{k}\geq\tau_{\mathcal{P}}]\geq\rho_{\mathcal{P}}\quad\forall i\in \mathcal{A}\text{ and }k\geq n_{\mathcal{P}},\] (4)

_where \(X_{i}^{k}=\min_{\text{arms }A\neq A_{\mathrm{cand}}}\mathbb{E}[\mu_{A_{ \mathrm{cand}}}-\mu_{A}|\mathcal{S}]\)_

